@Dad_of_Marine Yes, they are evil. They have imposed extreme sanctions upon their masses the way they have upon non-compliant nations. 

Food shortages, threat of evictions, little access to healthcare, businesses shut, jobs lost, economies crashed. Is this the West? Unbelievable.
@Dad_of_Marine Apparently, one mask is not enough - 'experts' are advising people to wear two. Maybe then it will be three, four..
